casebody.data:
Terry BUCHANAN
v.
David MITCHELL. No. 508P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 13, 2004. Terry Buchanan, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of NC. David Mitchell, Superintendent Mtn. View Corr. Inst., for Mitchell.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Plaintiff on the 4th day of October 2004 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Graham County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 13th day of October 2004."
